data.title: Bent Tree Golf Club
data.text:
Head PGA Golf Professional

Jeff Nielsen

Bent Tree Golf Course is excited to announce our new Head PGA Golf Professional, Jeff Nielsen. He comes to us with an abundance of passion and great experience in the golf world. He has been in the golf industry for the past 28 years. For 17 years he was at another local golf course where he focused on player development and has been a PGA member for the past 20 years. Servicing as the Duchesne women's golf coach for the past 12 years and under his leadership, they have won the Nebraska Women's State Tournament 5 times.

Jeff's personality is magnetic and he is a joy to be around. We look forward to him helping us take Bent Tree to the next level.

Golfweek Best Public Course Winner

Golfweek, which is owned and operated by USA Today Sports, annually updates the "Best Courses You Can Play" ranking. This ranking is determined by a nationwide panel of raters who evaluate courses on 10 criteria, scoring them from 1 to 10. These scores are then averaged to create Golfweekâ€™s Best course rankings.
